  notes:
    - "lodash.findlastkey exports the _.findLastKey function directly as module.exports."
    - "findLastKey(object, predicate) returns the key of the last matching element."
    - "Iterates in reverse insertion order."
    - "Returns undefined if not found (omitted from test vectors)."
